Democratic leaders
left Washington for a
stop in Berryville in

29:30.600 --> 29:35.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Northwest Virginia, estimated
population around 4,300.

29:35.433 --> 29:40.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
