needs to win back voters.

29:43.133 --> 29:45.066 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

29:45.066 --> 29:47.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHUCK SCHUMER (D-NY), Minority
Leader: When you lose elections,
as we did in 2014 and

29:47.600 --> 29:50.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
